---
title: Middle Eastern Roasted Chickpeas with Garlic Couscous & Mint Yoghurt
description: Go big or go home! That was our philosophy with the bold flavours in this veggie sensation. There’s chermoula roast veggies, plus chickpeas and a lightly seasoned couscous that's all brought together with a cooling mint yoghurt. Go big with us, you’ll be glad you did.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e6081a213a2130c9832e221-d53d3375.jpg
